程序包 projecttwo

类 Date

java.lang.Object
projecttwo.Date
所有已实现的接口:
Comparable<Date>
public class Date extends Object implements Comparable<Date>
This class is for the creation and manipulation of Date object. Date object holds information such as year, month, and day. Can also be created as the mm/dd/yyyy of the current day (i.e. today)
作者:
Kangwei Zhu, Michael Israel

    • Date

      public Date()
      This is a constructor method for Date class that creates an object with today’s date This method should be used when you need to know the current calendar date

    • Date

      public Date(String date)
      This is a constructor method for Date class that takes “mm/dd/yyyy” and creates a Date object This method should be used when you want to keep track of dob or expirations
      参数:
      date - The date in mm/dd/yyyy String format

      public int getDay()
      The method is used when getting the day of a Date.
      返回:
      the day of the desired Date

    • compareTo

      public int compareTo(Date date)
      This method compares the two date values(ignore case difference). Checks and compares the individual calendar year, month, and day
      指定者:
      compareTo 在接口中 Comparable<Date>
      参数:
      date - the date to be compared.
      返回:
      1 if first date greater than second, 0 if two dates are equal, -1 if first date smaller than second/

    • isLeapYear

      public boolean isLeapYear()
      This method checks if a year is a leap year.
      返回:
      true if date is a leap year, false otherwise

    • isValidDob

      public boolean isValidDob()
      This method checks if a date of birth is valid. Checks if older than 18, is a valid calendar date, not today or a future date
      返回:
      true if date given is a valid dob, false otherwise

    • isValidExpiration

      public boolean isValidExpiration()
      This method checks if a date of expiration is valid. Checks if date is a valid calendar date
      返回:
      true if date given is a valid date, false otherwise

    • isValid

      public boolean isValid()
      This method checks if a date is valid calendar date. checks if the year is greater or equal than 0 and smaller or equal to currentYear, the month is greater or equal to 0 and smaller or equal to 12, the day is greater or equal to 0 and (depends on month and if it's a leap year or not)
      返回:
      true if date given is a valid date, false otherwise

    • toString

      public String toString()
      The method is used when stringed version of a Date.
      覆盖:
      toString 在类中 Object
      返回:
      the date in “mm/dd/yyyy” String format

    • main

      public static void main(String[] args)
      The testBed main method for testing Date class's compareTo method. It will create a testBed object, and use the testDateIsValid() method to test if the isValid method will give the correct output
      参数:
      args - arguments that pass to the testbed main. At here should be no arguments.
